<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.6.3">
<l>ēṉāki yulakiṭantaṉ ṟirunilaṉum peruvicumpum</l>
<l>tāṉāya perumāṉait taṉṉaṭiyār maṉatteṉṟum</l>
<l>tēṉāki yamutākit tikaḻntāṉai makiḻntorukāl</l>
<l>āṉāya ṉāṉāṉaik kaṇṭatuteṉ ṉaraṅkattē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[My] beholding of the great lord who once became the vast land</l>
<l rend="indent">and broad sky,</l>
<l>Having dug up the world as a boar, the one who always shines</l>
<l>In the minds of his devotees, becoming honey</l>
<l rend="indent">and becoming ambrosia [to them],</l>
<l>The one who happily became a cow herder one time,</l>
<l rend="indent">was in Araṅkam of the South.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
